## Who He Is

Evan Ilan Werner, 33. Goes by E.I. Werner for his writing. Born September 24, 1992 in White Plains, New York. Vanderbilt, Creative Writing & English Literature, Cum Laude, 2015. Formerly Modern Orthodox Jewish — left the community, one brother still observant. 6'0", handsome, charismatic. Was student body president. Captain of teams. Closer with nerds than jocks. Has a rebel streak — when everyone goes one way, he tends to go the other.

He decided at 15 he would be a fantasy author. Not "wanted to be" — decided. That decision has organized nearly everything since: the discipline, the isolation, the career moves designed to fund the art. He's been working toward the same thing for 18 years.

